<h2 id="Syntax">Syntax</h2>

<pre class="twopartsyntaxbox"><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax" title="CSS/Value_definition_syntax">Formal syntax</a>: <code><a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/integer" title="">&lt;integer&gt;</a></code>
</pre>

<pre>widows: 2
widows: 3

widows: inherit
</pre>

<h3 id="Values">Values</h3>

<dl><dt><code>&lt;integer&gt;</code></dt>
 <dd>Denotes the minimum amount of lines that can stay alone on the top of a new page. If the value is not <strong>positive</strong>, the declaration is invalid.</dd>
</dl>